Edge Cases Handled
âœ” Empty matrix â†’ If matrix is empty or matrix[0] is empty, return false.
âœ” Single row matrix â†’ Works seamlessly as itâ€™s a continuous 1D search.
âœ” Target not present â†’ Returns false correctly.
âœ” Target at first/last element â†’ Efficiently finds it in O(log n) time.

